  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个源数据通路的架构图，核心是从系统内存读取数据，经过调度、AXI读引擎、SRAM控制器，最后从网络出口出去。最顶层我想叫\"Source Data Path\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "source_data_path",
        "SCHED",
        "AXI_RD",
        "SRAM_CTRL",
        "DRAIN",
        "NETWORK",
        "MEM"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，整体流向是从内存到网络出口。那Scheduler在这个通路里扮演什么角色？是发起读请求的吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SCHED",
        "MEM",
        "NETWORK"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，Scheduler负责调度，它会发出sched_rd_valid信号给AXI读引擎。等读完成，AXI_RD还要回一个sched_rd_done给Scheduler。我想把Scheduler的框用浅蓝色填充，突出它是控制起点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SCHED",
        "AXI_RD",
        "sched_rd_valid",
        "sched_rd_done"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，Scheduler和AXI读引擎的双向握手关系我记下了。AXI读引擎内部需要展开吗？还是作为一个黑盒？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SCHED",
        "AXI_RD"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "需要展开，AXI读引擎内部有AR Channel和R Channel，就是地址通道和数据通道。这个子图我想命名为\"axi_read_engine\"。另外，系统内存通过m_axi_ar/r接口连接到AXI_RD。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AXI_RD",
        "AR",
        "R",
        "MEM",
        "m_axi_ar/r"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "清楚了，AR和R是AXI标准通道。那AXI读引擎读完数据后，数据流向哪里？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AXI_RD",
        "AR",
        "R"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "数据通过fill_valid和data信号送给SRAM控制器。这个控制器比较复杂，我想单独做一个子图叫\"src_sram_controller\"，内部用从左到右的布局。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AXI_RD",
        "SRAM_CTRL",
        "fill_valid/data",
        "src_sram_controller"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "SRAM控制器内部结构能详细说一下吗？我看到你提到了unit，是有多个处理单元吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SRAM_CTRL"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的，内部有个\"Controller Units\"的子图，包含unit 0、unit 1到unit 7。这些单元之间用虚线连接，表示它们是流水线关系。另外还需要一个Channel Arbiter来做仲裁，所有units都连到ARB上。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SRAM_CTRL",
        "units",
        "U0",
        "U1",
        "U7",
        "ARB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，U0到U1到U7用虚线串联，然后都连到Channel Arbiter。那SRAM控制器处理完数据后怎么出去？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "U0",
        "U1",
        "U7",
        "ARB",
        "SRAM_CTRL"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "通过drain_valid和data信号送到Drain Interface。这个Drain Interface我打算用浅绿色填充，表示数据出口。然后Drain Interface再连到Network Egress。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SRAM_CTRL",
        "DRAIN",
        "NETWORK",
        "drain_valid/data"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "流程清楚了：内存→AXI读引擎→SRAM控制器→Drain→网络。系统内存的样式有什么要求吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "MEM",
        "AXI_RD",
        "SRAM_CTRL",
        "DRAIN",
        "NETWORK"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "系统内存用圆柱形表示，填充浅粉色。另外整个图的配色我想用自定义主题，主色调是#e8eaf6，边框用#3949ab。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "MEM",
        "theme",
        "primaryColor",
        "primaryBorderColor"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "主题配置我记下了。让我梳理一下目前的层级结构：最外层是Source Data Path，里面包含Scheduler、AXI_RD子图、SRAM_CTRL子图和Drain。AXI_RD内部有AR和R通道，SRAM_CTRL内部有units子图和ARB。对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "source_data_path",
        "SCHED",
        "AXI_RD",
        "SRAM_CTRL",
        "DRAIN",
        "AR",
        "R",
        "units",
        "ARB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，但漏了一个：SRAM_CTRL内部的units子图要包含U0、U1、U7这三个单元。另外units到ARB的连接关系要明确表示出来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "units",
        "U0",
        "U1",
        "U7",
        "ARB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "U0、U1、U7之间的虚线连接是U0连U1，U1连U7，还是U0同时连U1和U7？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "U0",
        "U1",
        "U7"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是链式连接：U0虚线连U1，U1再虚线连U7。表示数据在单元间逐级传递。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "U0",
        "U1",
        "U7"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了，链式虚线连接。现在检查信号流向：Scheduler发出sched_rd_valid给AXI_RD，AXI_RD回sched_rd_done；AXI_RD输出fill_valid/data给SRAM_CTRL；SRAM_CTRL输出drain_valid/data给DRAIN。还有遗漏吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "sched_rd_valid",
        "sched_rd_done",
        "fill_valid/data",
        "drain_valid/data"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "还有内存到AXI_RD的接口m_axi_ar/r，这个是AXI标准总线接口。另外DRAIN到NETWORK的连接比较简单，没有额外的信号标注。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "MEM",
        "AXI_RD",
        "m_axi_ar/r",
        "DRAIN",
        "NETWORK"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 20,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，所有连接都齐了。让我再确认一下样式：SCHED浅蓝(#e3f2fd)，DRAIN浅绿(#c8e6c9)，MEM浅粉(#fce4ec)。整体主题主色#e8eaf6，边框#3949ab。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SCHED",
        "DRAIN",
        "MEM",
        "style"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 21,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "等等，SRAM_CTRL内部的布局方向我刚才说的是LR（从左到右），但外面的Source Data Path整体是TB（从上到下）。这个要区分开。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "source_data_path",
        "SRAM_CTRL",
        "direction"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 22,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "收到，我修正一下：source_data_path用TB，SRAM_CTRL子图用LR，units子图没有指定方向就用默认。其他子图AXI_RD也用TB对吗？",
