    {
      "turn_id": 24,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "布局方向都设置好了。最后确认一下元素命名：Scheduler、axi_read_engine、src_sram_controller、Drain Interface、Network Egress、System Memory。units里的unit 0、unit 1、unit 7，以及AR Channel、R Channel、Channel Arbiter。",
      "elements_involved": [
